    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Needles used for sewing in the loose ends and joining pieces woven in different colors of a tapestry. Tapestry needles are long, strong, and blunt-ended with a long-shaped, wide eye.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
